se also tweeted that “awa South lo kan” — which means, “it is the turn of the South”. The former governor added that Nigerians should “await details soon”.   Ayodele Fayose By Biodun Busari  In a move many have interpreted as support for Bola Tinubu, the All Progressives Congress, APC, presidential candidate, former Ekiti State governor, Ayo Fayose, has said it was the turn of the South to produce the country’s President in 2023. Fayose, a chieftain of Peoples… In "Politics" The quest for ascendancy in the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP ahead of the 2023 presidential election primary was yesterday descending into war after supporters of two of the leading presidential contenders, Atiku Abubakar and Governor Nyesom Wike were engaged in a verbal war. In "News" 2023 Presidency: I'll embrace restructuring, advance creation of state police if elected - Wike In "News"